data.description: Welcome Home to this lovely 5 Bedroom, 3.5 baths including the newer finished lower level w/bonus room, bedroom and bath, great for teens or a mother-in-law suite, ample storage throughout, spacious open living room and kitchen with island and eating area for socializing, separate dining room or could be used as a large office, 2 car attached garage w/ even more storage, This home is beautifully located next to a wooded preserve and has a large private backyard for cookouts and entertaining friends, conveniently located within 13 minutes of the airport, shopping and downtown, walking distance to 3 New Westerville City schools in the neighborhood, nature trails, b-ball courts, dog park and a community pool.
